    <h1>Careers at blcnwht</h1>
    <p>At blcnwht, we are more than just a fashion brand—we are a community of passionate individuals committed to redefining style and sustainability. If you’re driven by creativity, innovation, and a desire to make a difference, we’d love to have you on our team.</p>

    <h2>Why Work With Us?</h2>
    <p>At blcnwht, we value our employees as much as our customers. We believe in fostering a positive and inclusive work environment where everyone’s contributions are recognized and rewarded. Our team members enjoy competitive salaries, comprehensive benefits, and opportunities for professional growth and development.</p>

    <h2>Current Openings</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Design & Product Development:</strong> Help shape the future of fashion with your creative vision.</li>
        <li><strong>Marketing & Communications:</strong> Spread the word about blcnwht through innovative marketing strategies.</li>
        <li><strong>Customer Service:</strong> Provide exceptional service to our customers and ensure their satisfaction.</li>
        <li><strong>Operations & Logistics:</strong> Keep our supply chain running smoothly and efficiently.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to Apply</h2>
    <p>If you’re interested in joining the blcnwht team, please send your resume and a cover letter to <a href="mailto:careers@blcnwht.com">careers@blcnwht.com</a>. Be sure to include the position you’re applying for in the subject line. We look forward to hearing from you!</p>

    <h2>Internships</h2>
    <p>We also offer internship programs for students and recent graduates looking to gain hands-on experience in the fashion industry. To apply, email your resume and cover letter to <a href="mailto:internships@blcnwht.com">internships@blcnwht.com</a>.</p>
